properties.description: this is the high court view for use in either PBI or the vanilla curated view

content.query:
IF NOT EXISTS ( SELECT  *
                FROM    sys.schemas
                WHERE   name = 'mipins' )
    EXEC('CREATE SCHEMA [mipins]');
GO

--CREATE VIEW FOR HIGH COURT--

CREATE OR ALTER VIEW mipins.vw_mipins_high_court
AS

SELECT DISTINCT

*

FROM [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].high_court_dim

GO
